Package org.scictrl.mp.orbitcorrect

Class ActionReportAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.scictrl.mp.orbitcorrect.ActionReportAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, IActionReportListener
public abstract class ActionReportAdapter extends Object implements IActionReportListener
An abstract adapter class for receiving component events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.
Author:
igor@scictrl.com
